	Vast: {
		DisplayName: Vast
		TooltipBase: The strength and effects of this accessory increase with progression
		Level0:
			'''
			8% reduced mana cost
			Automatically use mana potions when needed
			'''
		Level1:
			'''
			Mana potions restore 10% more mana
			While under the effects of [cebuff:CalamityEntropy/ManaVein], gain 4% increased magic critical strike chance
			'''
		Level2:
			'''
			Automatically uses mana potions, with 75% of the restoration applied instantly
			The remaining 25% is recovered over 5 seconds
			If you take damage exceeding 80 life during this period, the restoration is interrupted, extending invincibility frames and briefly accelerating life regeneration
			'''
		Level3: After consuming mana equivalent to 50% of your maximum mana, gain a stack of mana mania, which increases enhanced mana by 4% (stacks up to 5 times)
		Level4:
			'''
			Effects of [cbuff:ManaSickness] and [cbuff:CalamityMod/ManaBurn] are halved
			Every 2 stacks of mana mania grant 0.03% damage reduction
			Increases life regeneration when hit while restoring mana
			'''
		Level5:
			'''
			Critical hits inflict the [cebuff:CalamityEntropy/SoulDisorder] debuff on the target
			Upon mana depletion, attacks switch from consuming mana to restoring mana for 6 seconds
			Taking damage during this period extends invincibility frames
			'''
		Level6:
			'''
			At full stacks of mana mania, each mana depletion grants
			1% increased magic critical strike chance and 3% increased magic critical strike damage (stacks up to 5 times)
			'''
		Tooltip: The ebb and flow of mana itself pulses through your veins...
	}

