SmolderingSetBonus:
	'''
	Gain a demonic tail that attacks nearby enemies and inflicts [cbuff:OnFire3]
	Increases your maximum number of minions by 1
	+80 maximum stealth
	'''
ChaoticSetBonus:
	'''
	12% increased damage reduction
	12% increased damage
	+40 max life
	Increases your max number of minions by 3
	Releases three chaos cells on taking damage
	Cells will chase and attack enemies before returning and converting into 7 life each
	Press [KEY] to consume 80 life and spawn three cells
	You can have a maximum of [LIMIT] cells active at a time
	'''
VoidEaterBonus:
	'''
	Every three seconds, send three nihil beams on enemy hit that inflict [cebuff:CalamityEntropy/VoidVirus]
	Project a shield that can withstand [SHIELD] damage
	The nihility shield needs ten seconds to recover once broken
	Press [KEY] to consume 80 life and accelerate the shield's recovery
	Grants +1HP/s life regeneration while the shield is broken
	Increases your max number of minions by 2
	Maximum mana increased by 100
	14% increased damage and critical strike chance
	+120 maximum stealth
	'''
VoidEaterSet: Void Eater Set
ChaoticSet: Chaotic Set
NihArmorConnet:
	'''
	Aim at another player that is wearing the [ANOTHERSET] and press the [CONNECT] button to connect
	During connection, gain an additional 2HP/s of health regeneration
	The health of the player with lower health is extracted to provide healing for another player
	When receiving fatal damage, if the other party can withstand the damage, 
	it will be borne by the other party, and this effect has a cooldown time of 12 seconds
	When connected, both parties will acquire the ability of nihility shield and chaotic cells
	'''
LOCKED: " [LOCKED]:"
BCU1: Requires defeating King Slime
BCU2: Requires defeating Perforator or Hive Mind
BCU3: Requires defeating Wall of Flesh
BCU4: Requires defeating Plantera
BCC1: Right Click to extend thorny vines after a brief charge
BCC2:
	'''
	  Holding Right Click on a target pulls you toward it and deals impact damage
	  This skill consumes 20% of the Bramble Bar
	  Left Click swing hits slightly charge the Bramble Bar
	'''
BCC3:
	'''
	  Right Click then quickly Left Click to attach the weapon to the vines
	  While Left Click is held, the sword attaches to the struck target, 
	  Having the sword attached to an enemy grants continuous life steal that scales with the weapons level and slowly fills the Bramble Bar
	'''
BCC4:
	'''
	  Double tap and hold Right Click to throw the weapon,
	  While Right Click is held, the weapon rapidly pierces enemies near the cursor while continuously consuming Bramble Bar charge
	  Holding Left Click while the weapon is thrown spins the blade, releasing homing leaves
	'''
PrefixitemDesc: Right Click on a piece of armor with this to grant it a prefix
MariviniumSet:
	'''
	Increases your max number of minions by 10
	75% increased summon Damage
	+135 maximum stealth
	Increased life regeneration when standing still
	Immunity to most debuffs
	When holding a true melee weapon, gain 10% increased damage reduction and 15 defense
	Stealth strike has a probability of causing a water explosion
	Obtain 2 layers of shields, which will take 36 seconds to recover after being shattered
	After shields shatter, consume 100 life for 50% increased damage for 10 seconds
	'''
DeathMode: Death Mode
CdMantle: Holy Mantle Cooldown
MissileLauncherDescTooltip: Launch missiles that get lodged into enemies and cause damage over time
MissileLauncherMaxStickTooltip: Up to {0} can be lodged in the same enemy

