	'''
	A supreme predator born from the void, bearing a resemblance to that Devourer of Gods you once encountered.
	It feasts on order, spreads chaos, and tears the world apart as its hunting ground... and you are no prey to be devoured.
	'''
AbyssalWraithBestiary: ???
NihilityTwinBestiary:
	'''
	Basic entities of the void, emerging from the rifts, they have become enemies of order through mindless entropy.
	That realm follows survival rules utterly opposed to reality—which is why the conflict between reality and the void is a fight to the death.
	'''
CCellSmallBestiary: Small individuals produced by chaotic cell division, following the commands of their mother.
ProphetBestiary:
	'''
	A pitiful, shattered soul driven mad by the horrifying truth hidden behind the invasion of the void.
	Bound to ancient texts, it endlessly repeats mindless screams and whispers, desperately—yet futilely—trying to convey what it has witnessed.
	'''
LuminarisBestiary: Moths infected by astral exist with the purpose of spreading astral infection
ApsychosBestiary:
	'''
	The creature wandering in the depths of lava has a carapace made of crustal rocks.
	It may have been regarded as another way for sealing primoridial forces, but it has clearly failed.
	'''
WorldGen.VoidOreSpawn: Void energy is emanating from the sky

