vfb:
	'''
	Set Bonus: Gain a void charge bar
	Damaging enemies will fill the void charge bar
	Increases movement and flight speed based on the amount of void charge in the bar
	Press the Armor Set Bonus key when void charge is full to consume void charge and summon a Void Wraith to assist in battle
	The Void Wraith's damage type depends on the weapon in hand and grants indefinite flight for 10 seconds on spawn
	Increases armor penetration by 20
	'''
