DraedonDialogs: {
	Void: {
		Inquiry: The Void
		Response:
			'''
			The void has always been a subject of mine, long before I ever interacted extensively with this world.
			During my collaboration with Yharim, I proposed a more in-depth study of the Void, and therefore he went to find the best spiritual prophet of the land, who he had locked in the dungeon for dealing with the gods.
			Tests on the man led to a rather grim fate, however such results were no deterrent to my pursuit of knowledge.
			When Yharim learned of this, he expressed strong opposition, but I nevertheless opened a rift to the Void and deployed a reconnaissance drone. 
			Shortly after entering the Void, the transmission of footage was lost, leaving only static and ethereal whispers in its place.
			From then on, I was forbidden from further research without heavy oversight, which I cannot easilly obtain.
			Perhaps you shall truly explore this forbidden frontier.
			'''
	}
}

