	Leave a shadow when performing a teleport strike, the shadow will attack alongside you
	Slash dash will generate an additional slash perpendicular to the original
	Increased the healing value of steal strikes
	'''
TSU5: Need to kill Polterghast
TSA6: Leave behind a rift when dashing. The rift will continuously damaie enemies in radius
TSU6: Need to kill the Devourer of Gods
