AzafureSet:
	'''
	All azafure equipment receive enhancements to thier abilities
	Replaces adrenaline with the durability bar
	The Durability bar provides up to 12 defense and 16% damage reduction, while slowing your movement speed
	Durability is consumed based on damage taken when hit
	Durability slowly regenerates 5 seconds after taking damage
	When the durability bar is depleted, it becomes inactive and requires time to restore functionality
	'''
AzafureSet2:
	'''
	All azafure equipment receive enhancements to thier abilities
	Replaces adrenaline with the durability bar
	The durability bar provides up to 24 defense and 20% damage reduction
	Durability is consumed based on damage taken when hit
	Durability slowly regenerates 5 seconds after taking damage
	When the durability bar is depleted, it becomes inactive and requires time to restore functionality
	+80 maximum stealth
	10% increased movement speed
	Increases max number of minions by 1
	'''
AzafureSet3:
	'''
	Negates fall damage
	All azafure equipment receive enhancements to thier abilities
	Replaces adrenaline with the durability bar
	The durability bar provides up to 36 defense and 24% damage reduction
	Durability is consumed based on damage taken when hit
	Durability slowly regenerates 5 seconds after taking damage
	When the durability bar is depleted, it becomes inactive and requires time to restore functionality
	+120 maximum stealth
	Press [KEY] to transform into an acropolis mecha
	Press again to cancel the transformation
	The mecha can be activated after leaving it on a 1 minute cooldown
	When the mecha is activated, gain 15 defense and 10% damage reduction while inside
	While in the mecha only it's two weapons are available
	Left Click to attack, Right Click to switch between it's laser blade and homing missile forms
	The hook claw will be replaced by a harpoon
	Pressing the Grapple button while in the mech will launch a harpoon, pulling you towards the hooked object
	The harpoon will pull smaller enemies to the player and if it hooks onto bosses the player will be pulled to them
	'''
